{"tid":1298744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林奠出口術 五大訴求無一做到 愚弄香港人","createTime":"2019-07-09T02:34:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T02:52:56.000Z","uid":1167,"like":23,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"2cc891ecdbbbe05753ddc2508d32c8a4dc076250","tid":1298744,"uid":1167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"林奠對於五大訴求無一樣野做到<br />\n只係將上次講既野再講一次<br />\n呢個政府諗住愚弄香港人<br />\n等好多市民覺得政府已讓步<br />\n令抗爭者同大眾出現矛盾<br />\n想加劇我地香港人既內鬥<br />\n大家千奇唔好中計！<br />\n要加強文宣！等大家清楚政府詭計<br />\n如果我地有一絲覺得滿足於政府呢次聲明<br />\n咁我地仲對得住死去既抗爭者咩？<br />\n我地仲對得住我地既下一代？<br />\n我地呼吸既自由空氣只會慢慢失去！<br />\n我地要繼續為我地愛既香港<br />\n為自由、民主、普世價值而戰！<br />\n大家一定要繼續走下去！"},{"pid":"fd7159b9223b86033cf36536381845eff114b6b8","tid":1298744,"uid":145496,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:35:07.000Z","msg":"無錯，呢個柒婆信一成都死"},{"pid":"b9c8d41801343a586663ff29207aa8db2bdc5a64","tid":1298744,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢岩岩承認壽終正寢＝暫緩<br />\n<br />\n係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e22219430128cd48d9f1e7a11ce3350ef5785624","tid":1298744,"uid":1167,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"b9c8d41801343a586663ff29207aa8db2bdc5a64","tid":1298744,"uid":143343,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:35:15.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">佢岩岩承認壽終正寢＝暫緩<br />\n<br />\n係一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T02:37:06.000Z","msg":"撒回先係正式有法律效力字眼，唔好俾柒婆呃到！"},{"p